---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
const yearsOfExperience = new Date().getFullYear() - 2018;
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    As a graduate from UBC with a Bachelors Degree in Computer Science and a
    software engineer with over {yearsOfExperience} years of professional experience
    in full-stack web development. I have worked in different projects and technologies,
    from small websites to big applications and microservices. I have experience
    in the whole development process, from the design to the deployment. I am a fast
    learner and I am always looking for new challenges.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="UBC"
      subtitle="2011 to 2017 at University of British Columbia, Vancouver, Canada"
    >
      Graduated from UBC, the University of British Columbia, with a Bachelors
      Degree in Science, majoring in Computer Science. Graudated with a Co-op
      Option.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
